# Ephemeral QA environment

1. **No assumed production URLs**: QA does not require a purchased prod domain or paid static hosting URL.
2. **Compile-time archive origin**: Courier links use **`WEB_ARCHIVE_BASE_URL`** via `--dart-define` / `dart_defines.json` — never silently override when the compiler define is non-empty (see `vault_service_io.dart`).
3. **Tunnel awareness**: Use an HTTPS tunnel (e.g. Ngrok) exposing local Flutter Web on `:3000`; paste that origin into `WEB_ARCHIVE_BASE_URL` before building the iOS app that shares links.
